correctness.rationale: Major factual mismatches, invented values, and at least one schema violation. Key issues: (1) Schema violation: processParameters.plasmaPower is set to null, but the schema expects an object if present—omit it instead. (2) Dosing/purge times: Article states 2 s dosing and 8 s evacuation, but extraction uses 2 ms and 8 ms (wrong by 10^3 and not traceable). Should be 2000 ms and 8000 ms if using the schema’s MilliSEC unit. (3) Flow rates: Article reports DEZn and H2O flows in μmol/min (e.g., 52.8 and 24.2 μmol/min); extraction assigns those numbers to unit SCM-PER-MIN (volumetric), causing unit/type inconsistency. (4) Pressure: Article 0.09–0.10 Torr; extraction 0.095 with unit MilliM_HG appears intended as mmHg, acceptable numerically. (5) GPC, number of cycles, nucleationPeriod: values (1 Å/cycle, 2000 cycles, 5 cycles) are not reported in the article—fabricated and not traceable. (6) Material/electrical properties: Resistivity is misconverted—article’s 6.4×10^-4 Ω·cm corresponds to 6.4×10^-6 Ω·m, but extraction uses 6.4×10^-4 Ω·m (100× too high). Carrier density given as 1.5×10^19 m^-3 is off by many orders from reported ~10^19 cm^-3 (should be ~10^25 m^-3). Mobility 30 cm^2/V·s is for undoped films, yet resistivity reported corresponds to B-doped films—internally inconsistent. (7) Film thickness and conditions: The extraction mixes B-doped (≈200 nm) and undoped (mobility 30 cm^2/V·s) results in one process, instead of separate processes; B2H6 dopant flow and timing (central to the study) are omitted from reactantSelection/flowRates and supercycle/timing. (8) Numerous properties are invented without support: refractive index, absorption, band gap/method, uniformity %, conformality aspect ratio, elemental concentrations/ratios by XPS, crystallinity by XRD, roughness (AFM), film density (XRR), and all TFT deviceProperties—none are in the article. (9) PurgingGas: Article describes evacuation between steps; an argon purge is not specified—‘purgingGas: Ar’ is not traceable. Corrections needed: remove or correct unsupported/invented values; fix time units (2 s → 2000 ms, 8 s → 8000 ms); express flow rates with correct units (μmol/min) per schema or provide justified conversion; correct resistivity and carrier density units/magnitudes; add dopant (B2H6) selection, flow, and timing if representing B-doped process; or split into distinct undoped and B-doped processes; ensure all fields are traceable and schema-compliant.

completeness.rationale: Largely incomplete and not traceable to the article. Key issues: (1) Multiple processes not captured: the paper reports both undoped ZnO ALD (105–165 °C, ~220 nm films) and B-doped ZnO ALD with varying B2H6/DEZn ratios and four distinct doping sequences (A–D). Only one process is provided, and the B2H6 injection schemes and ratios are absent. (2) Missing dopant in reactants: B2H6 (diluted in H2) is used and specific flow (e.g., 0.42 μmol/min) is reported, but it is not included in reactantSelection or flowRates; only DEZn and H2O are listed. (3) Time and flow units incorrect: dosing/purge times are 2 s and 8 s in the article but recorded as 2 ms and 8 ms (should be 2000 ms and 8000 ms to comply with schema). Flow rates are given in μmol/min in the article but encoded as SCM-PER-MIN; units and magnitudes are therefore wrong. (4) Electrical properties inconsistent and unit errors: resistivity 6.4×10^-4 Ω·cm (B-doped) was entered as 0.00064 Ω·m (100× too large); mobility 30 cm^2/V·s pertains to undoped 220 nm films but is mixed with B-doped resistivity (mobility actually decreases with B2H6); carrier density values are in cm^-3 in the article but provided in PER-M3 with unconverted magnitudes. (5) Numerous values fabricated/not traceable: refractive index, absorption, band gap, uniformity, conformality, elemental composition/XPS, crystallinity/XRD, roughness/AFM, film density/XRR, and all TFT device properties are not reported in the article. (6) Schema issues: plasmaPower is set to null (invalid type), and thicknessControl fields (numberofCycles, filmThickness) are incorrectly nested inside growthPerCycle; growth-per-cycle (1 Å) and 2000 cycles are not reported and thus not traceable. (7) Pressure is reported as a range (0.09–0.10 Torr) but a single value is chosen without citation. To improve, add separate undoped and B-doped processes (including B2H6 reactant, its flow or cycle ratio, and doping sequences A–D), correct all units (time in ms, flows in proper QUDT units or convert), fix electrical property units/values, remove unreported properties, and align schema nesting.
